      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAST FREDDY (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 1.5 lengths second (23.69) over 407m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Rates highly and will give a great sight. NUKA (7) ran below best last time finishing seventh (29.52) over 498m at Townsville from Box 4. Has ability and is one of the better chances. REGAL WOLF (3) has a strong record this track and trip with 10 wins and seven placings from 27 starts. Hit the frame latest (23.54) when second at this track in a Free For All. Can feature in the finish. LEGENDS TOLD (2) comes off a (23.85) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 407m at this track. Has one wins already from this draw.",
